---
<section id="about" class="about-section page-section">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="profile-icon">
        {/* Placeholder for the profile icon */}
      </div>
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>
        Fully committed to the philosophy of life-long learning, I'm a full stack developer with a deep passion for JavaScript,
        React and all things web development. The unique combination of creativity, logic, technology and never
        running out of new things to discover, drives my excitement and passion for web development. When I'm
        not at my computer I like to spend my time reading, keeping fit and playing guitar.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-icons">
      {/* Placeholder for the technology icons */}
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
      <div class="tech-icon"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <style>
    .about-section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .about-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .profile-icon {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .tech-icons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .tech-icon {
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #fff;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</section>